org.dotplot.core.plugins
Class PluginIntegrationTaskPart

java.lang.Object
  org.dotplot.core.services.AbstractTaskPart
      org.dotplot.core.plugins.PluginIntegrationTaskPart
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, ITaskPart, ExecutionUnit
public class PluginIntegrationTaskPart
extends AbstractTaskPart

This TaskPart integrates Plugins into a PluginContext.

It is basicly done by invoking the installPlugin() method of the PluginContext.

Author:
Christian Gerhardt
See Also:
IPluginContext, IPluginContext#installPlugin(P), PluginIntegrationService
